	   <tr><td colspan=2>Say what?<br>These move pretty quick at 150pp for me.&nbsp;&nbsp;These are excellent twink/low/mid level gloves for rangers (love that dex for archery, fletching, weapon skills and mana is nice too), shadow knights (dex for channeling skill + almost 3 lifespikes or a lifedraw worth of mana), rogues and bards.  The falling price on gauntlets of the black is squeezing the pally market and warriors are probably better off with crafted, but these are solid for the other classes that can use em.  Of course on an older server, folks will likely have something better by their high 30s when they can get em but that doesn't mean they're junk.<br><br>My only problem with these is that clerics + shammies can't use them ... probably see em going for ~300 if they could.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
